Tidak! Gerbang akan segera terbuka.
Keluarkan mereka yang beriman!

42
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:10,210
Jangan biarkan mereka mendekati gerbang!

43
00:04:10,210 --> 00:04:12,190
Cobaan Dewi dihentikan!

44
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,190
Segeralah keluar!

45
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:22,830
Kalian semua juga bisa terkena imbasnya.
Segeralah keluar...

46
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:23,880
Eh?

47
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,280
Apa maumu?

48
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,930
Wawawa...

49
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:32,090
Ka... Kalian!

50
00:04:32,090 --> 00:04:36,160
Jangan-jangan kalian adalah Shadow Garden?

51
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:42,050
Maaf, tapi jadilah anak baik
hingga gerbangnya tertutup,

52
00:04:42,710 --> 00:04:44,210
wahai para putri.

53
00:04:46,090 --> 00:04:47,580
Sisanya kuserahkan padamu.

54
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:50,190
Dimengerti, Nona Alfa.

55
00:04:50,890 --> 00:04:52,890
Sejak kapan kau?

56
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:56,670
Delta.

57
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:58,300
Siap.

58
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,740
Dia adalah Alfa.

59
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:07,990
Dia lebih kuat dari kakakku.

60
00:05:17,890 --> 00:05:18,630
Hilang?

61
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:21,430
Tunggu! Jangan masuk ke wilayah suci!

62
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:24,770
Apa niat kalian sebenarnya?

63
00:05:24,770 --> 00:05:27,600
Kami hanya ingin kalian tetap tenang dan diam,

64
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,740
hingga gerbang itu tertutup.

65
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:32,840
Tapi si botak itu ikut dengan kami.

66
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,770
Ada urusan apa kalian ke wilayah suci?

67
00:05:35,770 --> 00:05:37,470
Bukan ada urusan apa,

68
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:39,230
tapi ada apa di sana.

69
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,530
Jangan bergerak.

70
00:05:42,090 --> 00:05:45,470
Aku tak tahu nasib orang ini
kalau kalian bergerak.

71
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:48,690
Kak Natsume!

72
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:50,310
Korbankan dia juga boleh, tuh.

73
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,510
Jangan!

74
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:53,670
Aku tidak apa-apa, kok!

75
00:05:53,670 --> 00:05:54,690
Mencurigakan.

76
00:05:54,690 --> 00:05:56,870
- Aku paham perasaan itu.
- Aku tidak apa-apa!

77
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,170
Kak Natsume!

78
00:05:58,170 --> 00:06:00,890
- Dia kelihatan sengaja.
- Kita bisa seenaknya masuk.

79
00:06:00,890 --> 00:06:03,350
Tapi belum tentu akan terus terbuka.

80
00:06:03,350 --> 00:06:04,340
Korbankan saja.

81
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:07,630
Kita menuju internal gereja. Sini, botak.

82
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:09,060
Wanita itu juga.

83
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:12,050
Kalau mau ke sana, pergi saja sendiri!

84
00:06:12,050 --> 00:06:13,770
Menuju dunia itu!

85
00:06:17,610 --> 00:06:20,520
Bereskan dia, Algojo Venom!

86
00:06:31,350 --> 00:06:32,990
Kau ingin kekuatan?

87
00:06:35,890 --> 00:06:39,870
Demi kemenangan yang alami!

88
00:06:45,670 --> 00:06:47,670
Aku takkan tumbang,

89
00:06:47,670 --> 00:06:50,380
di tempat seperti ini!

90
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:58,450
Apa? Kenapa? Venom!

91
00:06:58,450 --> 00:07:00,730
Sedang apa kau, Venom...

92
00:07:02,930 --> 00:07:04,240
Kau lihat?

93
